name: Escape
description:
When we were kids we ran away all the time. We didn't run away like pranks, not like those who skipped school or left home without warning. We ran away from ourselves, from our reality. It was hard because we were very young with an awareness of the things we were trying to forget. It was enough that someone invented a game or proposed a run to leave everything behind and escape. 

Cuando eramos chicos escapabamos todo el tiempo. No nos escapabamos como travesuras, no como quienes se salian del colegio o se iban de sus casas sin avisar. Nos esquivabamos a nosotros mismos, a nuestra realidad. Era duro porque eramos muy chicos con consciencia de las cosas que intentabamos olvidar. Bastaba que alguien inventará un juego o propusiera una corrida para dejar todo atrás y escapar.
